title: 'Caravan' migrants wait and see as few reach U.S.
text:
'Caravan' migrants wait and see as few reach U.S. 9:57am EDT - 01:36
U.S. border officials processed a trickle of asylum applications on Tuesday from a caravan of Central American migrants camped at the U.S.-Mexico border, despite criticism from U.S. President Donald Trump of their attempt to enter the country. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
